'''''Star Wars Weekly'' 4''' is the fourth issue in the ''[[Star Wars Weekly]]'' series of comic reprints.

==Contents==
*[[Star Wars (1977) 2|''Star Wars'' (1977) 2]] {{C|Part 2}}
*"[[w:c:marvel:Unknown Worlds of Science Fiction Vol 1 2|War Toy]]" {{C|Part 1}}

*"Behind the Scenes of ''Star Wars''" {{C|excerpt from ''[[Star Wars Official Collector's Edition]]''}}
*"Star Wars Glossary" {{C|excerpt from ''[[Star Wars Official Collector's Edition]]''}}
*A competition to win one of forty-eight jigsaw puzzles. To enter, the reader must match a pair of two identical [[R2-D2]]'s.

